<h3 class="h5 mt-4">Tips for success</h3>

<div class="card border-success mt-3">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-star text-warning"></i> Best practices</h4>
        <ul class="mb-0">
            <li><strong>Start simple:</strong> Don't try to add everything at once. Start with high-priority items and build up over time.</li>
            <li><strong>Be consistent:</strong> Update COMPASS regularly (weekly is ideal). It's more useful when kept current.</li>
            <li><strong>Use clear titles:</strong> Make titles descriptive so others can understand at a glance.</li>
            <li><strong>Add notes:</strong> Use description fields to provide context - your future self will thank you!</li>
            <li><strong>Link related items:</strong> Connect actions to their risks or issues to show relationships.</li>
            <li><strong>Update status:</strong> Keep statuses current so your dashboard accurately reflects reality.</li>
            <li><strong>Use filters:</strong> Don't get overwhelmed by long lists - use filters to focus on what matters now.</li>
            <li><strong>Check your dashboard daily:</strong> Make it part of your morning routine to review your dashboard.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

